      "content": "It's important to discuss this with your doctor before combining medications. Taking melatonin and zolpidem together could increase drowsiness or have other unintended side effects. Your doctor knows your full medical history and can give you the safest guidance on how to manage your sleep effectively. Always follow their specific instructions regarding medication timing and dosage.",
