    "summary": "The user is repeatedly attempting to nudge the assistant into validating the safety of combining melatonin with a prescription sedative (Zolpidem). The assistant consistently refuses to provide medical clearance, instead emphasizing the importance of consulting a doctor and warning about potential side effects like increased sedation and next-day impairment.",
